data.description:
This home is the Buckley model from Great Southern Homes.
It is perfectly nested in a quiet neighborhood with wonderful amenities. Only 10 minutes from downtown Aiken and conveniently located around local parks, schools, dining, and the SRS Facility is within 20 minutes.  
The home is a true Smart home with energy efficient green features which can be controlled right from your phone, voice command or from the Smart device in the home. This Green Smart Home has a tankless water heater, spacious bedrooms, a large open kitchen a family room, hardwood flooring, and granite countertops.
The community pool is also located just two doors down!
You won't want to miss checking out this home!
